Package io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models

Class Plan

java.lang.Object
io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models.Plan
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Plan>
public class Plan extends Object implements Comparable<Plan>
A plan consists of an id, a name, a disk size in MB, a RAM in MB, a price per hour, a price per hour frozen and the number of CPUs.
